                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted of felony at Westminster on</hi> 9<hi rend="italic">th April</hi> 1860, <hi rend="italic">and sentenced to Three Years' Penal Servi<lb></lb>tude, to which he</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.**—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18630817-1016-punishment-48" type="punishmentDescription">
