                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1016-18630817 t18630817-1016-punishment-48"></join>Six Years' Penal Servitude</rs>. The Jury stated that they did not believe one word of the evidence given by Thomas Taylor for the defence.</hi>
